title: MFSL UDSACD 2100 - 2111 (24-48) PACK# 13 ALAC
description:
This is the 13th of 17 packs for your holiday listening pleasure.

They have all been taken from ISO files. Extracted with Scarlet Book Extract as DSD files. Then sampled to 24-48 wav files with Saracon. Then ALACed with Xrecode II.

There are only 10 missing. This does include the only SACD done by MFSL prior to closing in 2000 and the Discovery and surround series (In Stereo), as well as the sampler.

The artwork will be in the last pack which includes the covers used from Mofi.

Enjoy!
